          "text": "Return Value",
          "type": "heading"
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "An attributed string that contains the characters from "
            },
            {
              "type": "codeVoice",
              "code": "str"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": " and the attributes specified by "
            },
            {
              "type": "codeVoice",
              "code": "attributes"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": ". The result is "
            },
            {
              "type": "codeVoice",
              "code": "NULL"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": " if there was a problem in creating the attributed string. Ownership follows the "
            },
